results.name: Signature-permutation of a Catalan automorphism: composition of A069771 and A125976.
comment: Like A069771, A069772, A125976 and A126313/A126314, this automorphism keeps symmetric Dyck paths symmetric, but not necessarily same.
link: A. Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2055
Index entries for signature-permutations of Catalan automorphisms
xref: Inverse: A126316. a(n) = A069771(A125976(n)) = A126290(A069771(n)) = A126313(A057164(n)). The number of cycles, number of fixed points and maximum cycle sizes in range [A014137(n-1)..A014138(n-1)] of this permutation are given by A127281, A127282 and A127283. See also the comment at A127280.
results.author: _Antti Karttunen_, Jan 16 2007
